<h3>Features</h3>
<ul>
    <li>Stunning fullscreen background Login Pages</li>
    <li>Restyles Login, Register & Reset Passwort Pages and the Interim Login Dialog</li>
    <li>13 Stunning fullscreen background images already included</li>
    <li>Use your own background image</li>
    <li>Choose from various Premade Styles to get a jumpstart</li>
    <li>50+ Customization Options</li>
    <li>Automatic plugin updates</li>
    <li>Full support for all major browsers</li>
    <li>Localization ready (.pot file included)</li>
    <li>Free future updates, to support even more features and customization options</li>
</ul>


